                        <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">Medium dark brown papyrus; broken off at the left and top; right and bottom margins are preserved; the papyrus was folded twice horizontally and three times vertically; it suffered damage at the surface; minor loss at the top to left, probably blank portion, as a result of the upper fold; holes and lacunae at several parts; there is no kollesis.</ab>
